News.Title: Kabra Jewels: Stellar Market Debut with 90% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Kabra Jewels shares listed at ₹243 on NSE SME, a 90% premium over the IPO price of ₹128. The stock further rallied to ₹255.35, nearly doubling investor wealth on the first day. The ₹40 crore IPO was oversubscribed 356 times, with strong demand across investor categories.
